metadata.name: Down The Rabbit Hole - Genesis Edition X Maxximillian
metadata.description:
Down The Rabbit Hole is the genesis in a multiple edition series. 


'What is this...?!   
We have to know!  
So down the rabbit hole we go!'


A few words of encouragement from the artist...  
Your own genuine curiosity, lovingly indulged, can be the best catalyst for all the good experiences you've ever dreamed of actually happening in your real life. The greatest luxury you can offer yourself and the world is to dedicate time each day to explore what you genuinely find irresistibly interesting—even if it seems to serve no purpose. Explore it because you are curious—the application of your discovery may later be revealed to you, or to someone who comes along after you. Humankind's most useful discoveries were discovered by accident. Why not yours?!
